Generate Design

Source: R/generate_design.R
generate_design.Rd

Generate design of presentation order based on Williams design.

generate_design(n_panelist, product, use_coding = TRUE)

Arguments

n_panelist

number of panelist
product

a numeric value of number or product or vector of product names
use_coding

wheteher to generate random three digit number for labeling

Value

Returns a dataframe of sensory design with Panelist column and Order of product presentation columns

Examples

generate_design(n_panelist = 10, product = letters[1:14], use_coding = FALSE)
